<ab facs="#facs_180_r1l10">
<del rend="strikethrough">hat vns Laurencʒ Groland <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> furgelegt / vvie </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_180_r1l11">Vnd als wir euch <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals von <expan>Laurencʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Grolands </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_180_r1l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie Jm auch etvvieuil </ab>
