<ab facs="#facs_180_r1l14">
<del rend="strikethrough">derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> darümb </del> darümb Er <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_180_r1l15">cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit kümt / vnd euch das <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wirdt </ab>
